odase.concurrency

Class ConcurrencyException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • odase.concurrency.ConcurrencyException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ConcurrencyException
extends RuntimeException
    An exception related to concurrent programming. This exception extends the RuntimeException class and therefore is not subject to Java's 'checked exceptions' making it a lot easier to use. Especially since we have not assigned any particular semantics to the InterruptedException that may be thrown by Java's concurrency support.
